---

<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-kicker">
      <span class="kicker-line">Senior Software Engineer & Coffee Addict // New York City</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">
      <span class="hero-line" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">Eric</span>
      <span class="hero-line" style="animation-delay: 0.3s; font-style: italic;">Qiu.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-bio">
      I build distributed systems and cloud infrastructure at Bloomberg.
      University of Waterloo CS. Previously at Addepar, Postmates, and BMO Capital Markets.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-bio hero-bio-aside" style="animation-delay: 0.45s">
      Outside work: pour over coffee, a Fujifilm X100VI, and whatever book is currently face-down on my desk.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="https://photos.ericqiu.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
         class="hero-link link-underline">I also shoot photos →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 120px 25px 80px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    min-height: auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
    animation: line-reveal 0.5s var(--transition-reveal) 0s both;
  }

  .kicker-line {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.05em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    font-optical-sizing: auto;
    font-feature-settings: "liga" 1, "dlig" 1;
  }

  .hero-line {
    display: block;
    animation: line-reveal 0.6s var(--transition-reveal) both;
  }

  .hero-bio {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    animation: line-reveal 0.6s var(--transition-reveal) 0.35s both;
  }

  .hero-bio-aside {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    animation: line-reveal 0.5s var(--transition-reveal) 0.5s both;
  }

  .hero-link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 90px 25px 60px;
    }

    .hero-name {
      font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 16vw, 4rem);
    }
  }
</style>
